hu.akarnokd.rxjava3.operators

Class Completables

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.akarnokd.rxjava3.operators.Completables

  • public final class Completables
extends Object
    Additional operators in the form of CompletableConverters, use Completable.to(CompletableConverter) to apply the operators to an existing sequence.
    Since:
    0.20.2
    See Also:
